docs.snippet: Hundreds of residents of Hong Kong, the Chinese-ruled territory rocked by street protests demanding free elections in 2014, have flown to Taiwan for Saturday's elections to see free-wheeling democracy in action....
docs.lead_paragraph: Hundreds of residents of Hong Kong, the Chinese-ruled territory rocked by street protests demanding free elections in 2014, have flown to Taiwan for Saturday's elections to see free-wheeling democracy in action.

headline.main: Hong Kong 'Umbrella Soldiers' Visit Boisterous Taiwan to See Democracy at Work
headline.print_headline: Hong Kong 'Umbrella Soldiers' Visit Boisterous Taiwan to See Democracy at Work

docs.snippet: Venezuela's Supreme Court on Monday declared that the new opposition-dominated congress' decisions are void until it unseats three barred lawmakers, bringing the country closer to a showdown over power in the legislature....
docs.lead_paragraph: Venezuela's Supreme Court on Monday declared that the new opposition-dominated congress' decisions are void until it unseats three barred lawmakers, bringing the country closer to a showdown over power in the legislature.

headline.main: Venezuelan High Court Declares Opposition Congress Null
headline.print_headline: Venezuelan High Court Declares Opposition Congress Null
